'''本·吉利兰''' ({{Lang-en|Ben Gilliland}}；{{bd|1976年|1月30日}}）是一位[[英国|英国]]图片编辑和科普作家，出生于[[達勒姆郡|達勒姆郡]][[达灵顿|达灵顿]]，工作生活在[[西薩塞克斯郡|西薩塞克斯郡]][[东普雷斯顿|东普雷斯顿]]，2015年起担任[[帕特里克·穆爾|帕特里克·穆爾]]所创立的''Astronomy Now'' 杂志编辑<ref>{{cite web|title=Previous winners of the Sir Arthur Clarke Awards 2005-2015|url=http://www.bis-space.com/2013/04/05/9719/sir-arthur-clarke-awards-2005-2014|website=British Interplanetary Society|publisher=British Interplanetary Society|access-date=2020-10-15|archive-date=2016-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220201041/http://www.bis-space.com/2013/04/05/9719/sir-arthur-clarke-awards-2005-2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>，主要作品有《从大爆炸到大终结》（''How to Build a Universe: From the Big Bang to the End of the Universe''，2015）等<ref>{{cite web |title=从大爆炸到大终结 |url=https://book.douban.com/subject/27103957/ |publisher=湖南科学技术出版社 |date=2017 |access-date=2020-10-15 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020000305/https://book.douban.com/subject/27103957/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Cong da bao zha dao da zhong jie = How to build a universe: from the big bang to the end of the universe |publisher=Hu nan ke xue ji shu chu ban she |location=Zhangsha |isbn=9787535793003 |edition=Di 1 ban}}</ref>。

